<div style="width:0;height:0;clear:both"></div><dl class="lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle-">
<dd class="lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle-title">
<span class="lemma-pinyin">
<span class="text">[fān jiāng dǎo hǎi]</span>
<a class="speak" href="javascript:;" id="j-pinyin-speak" nslog-type="10000106" title="点击发声"> </a>
</span>
<div id="fmp_flash_div" style="position:absolute; left:-9999px;">
<audio id="audio" src=""></audio>
</div>
<h1>翻江倒海</h1>
<a class="edit-lemma cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-edit-link" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="lock-lemma" href="javascript:;" nslog-type="10003105" target="_blank" title="锁定"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_lock-lemma"></em>锁定</a>
<a class="lemma-discussion cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-discussion-link" href="/planet/talk?lemmaId=1414917" nslog-type="90000102" target="_blank"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_discussion-solid"></em>讨论<span class="num">999</span></a>
</dd>
</dl><div class="promotion-declaration">
</div><div class="lemma-summary" label-module="lemmaSummary">
<div class="para" label-module="para">翻江倒海，读音fān jiāng dǎo hǎi，是一个成语，意思是形容水势浩大，比喻力量或声势非常壮大。代指非常艰难的事情。<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":1," data-sup="1">
[1]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[1]_78289"> </a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="configModuleBanner">
</div><div class="basic-info cmn-clearfix">
<dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-left">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">中文名</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
翻江倒海
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">外文名</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
overturning rivers and seas―overwhelming; stupendous
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">拼    音</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
fān jiāng dǎo hǎi
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">释    义</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
比喻力量或声势非常壮大
</dd>
</dl><dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-right">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">近义词</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
 <a href="/item/%E6%8E%92%E5%B1%B1%E5%80%92%E6%B5%B7" target="_blank">排山倒海</a>、<a href="/item/%E7%A7%BB%E5%B1%B1%E5%80%92%E6%B5%B7" target="_blank">移山倒海</a>
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">常用程度</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
常用
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">感情色彩</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
褒义词
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">成语结构</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
联合式
</dd>
</dl></div>
